snippet.title: Finnish Cottage 8 - TRAILER - Coming soon 2025
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on STEAM (link in bio)  
We didn't have a job so we made this game.
Welcome to Finnish Cottage 8, a classic Finnish summer cottage to die for! If you want to leave alive, you must identify whether or not an anomaly is in the house. Succeed 8 times in a row, and it may let you out...
Finnish Cottage 8 is an anomaly-hunting game on PC, based on real Finnish cottages. It's available now for wishlist on Steam with a full release in Q1 2025!
